A shocking video of a schoolgirl being violently assaulted by a male schoolmate, at what is believed to be a KwaZulu-Natal school, has surfaced on social media.ADVERTISINGinRead invented by Teads
In the video, the boy throws the girl against the wall. She falls to the ground and he kicks her repeatedly, before walking away.
The girl struggles to get up.
She appears to be bleeding.
The two looked to be in high school.
They were both wearing school uniforms in the video and it appeared to have been filmed on school premises.
When it was filmed and the name of the school – thought to be in Zululand – was not immediately clear.
But the video, which surfaced on Twitter on Women's Day, has drawn strong reaction from the public.












